  <name>Terminal</name>
  <summary>A pretty terminal for GNOME</summary>

  <developer_name>Paulo Queiroz</developer_name>

  <recommends>
    <control>pointing</control>
    <control>keyboard</control>
  </recommends>

  <description>
    <p>
      Terminal is a native terminal emulator for GNOME that offers superb
      theming options.
    </p>
    <p>With Terminal you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Set colors schemes and integrate them with the rest of the window</li>
      <li>Customize font and size</li>
      <li>Fully hide the window headerbar</li>
      <li>Quickly open links and files by ctrl+clicking file paths and URLs</li>
      <li>Easily paste file paths by dragging them into the window</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This app is written in Vala and uses GTK 3, libhandy, and VTE. An effort will be made to port to GTK 4 once VTE is ported too.
    </p>
  </description>

